  "onboarding.slide1_title": "🍂 What is Chaput?",
  "onboarding.slide1_subtitle": "Chaput is a social platform where people can discover conversations between other people.\n\nLeave a Chaput, start a conversation, and explore the conversations people create.",
  "onboarding.slide2_title": "🪢 Tie a Chaput",
  "onboarding.slide2_subtitle": "Leave a one-sentence Chaput on someone's profile.\n\nWhen the other person replies, the Chaput turns into a conversation and the story begins.\n\nThe conversation can only be viewed by users who follow at least one of the two profiles involved.",
  "onboarding.slide3_title": "⏳ The 24-Hour Rule",
  "onboarding.slide3_subtitle": "Every Chaput waits for a reply for only 24 hours.\n\nIf no reply arrives within that time, the Chaput is moved to the archive and loses its visibility.",
  "onboarding.slide4_title": "🌱 Revive",
  "onboarding.slide4_subtitle": "Some conversations deserve a second chance.\n\nUse Revive to reactivate an archived Chaput and give it another opportunity to receive a reply.",
  "onboarding.slide5_title": "🎭 Hidden Chaput",
  "onboarding.slide5_subtitle": "You don't have to reveal your identity to everyone.\n\nWhen you send a Hidden Chaput, your identity is visible only to the recipient.",
  "onboarding.slide6_title": "🤫 Whisper",
  "onboarding.slide6_subtitle": "Some messages should remain between two people.\n\nMessages sent using Whisper can only be seen by the two participants in the conversation. You can safely share personal information such as an address, phone number, email address, or social media account.",
  "onboarding.slide7_title": "💎 Super Chaput",
  "onboarding.slide7_subtitle": "Want your message to stand out?\n\nSuper Chaputs are highlighted more prominently than regular Chaputs.",
  "onboarding.slide8_title": "👀 Who Can See Conversations?",
  "onboarding.slide8_subtitle": "Only participants can send messages in a conversation.\n\nOther users can read conversations and react to messages.",
  "onboarding.slide9_title": "🌳 Get to Know People Through Their Conversations",
  "onboarding.slide9_subtitle": "Profile photos don't always tell the whole story.\n\nDiscover people through the conversations they have with others.",
  "feedback.sheet_subtitle": "Draw on the screenshot and add a short note.",
